Package: TextAnalysisR
Title: Text Mining Workflow Tools
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Mikyung", "Shin", , "shin.mikyung@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7907-9193"))
Description: 'TextAnalysisR' provides a supporting workflow for text mining analysis. The web app incorporates 'quanteda' (text preprocessing), 'stm' (structural topic modeling), and 'ggraph' as well as 'widyr' (network analysis). 'tidytext' was implemented to tidy non-tidy format objects.
